# 微信机器人重构计划

Try to refactoring the WechatRobot


## 进度
2023-12-23 这只是一个demo,接入了sqlite数据库,用于存储数据,完成了基本的消息接收的功能,并且区分了个人消息和群消息的处理。

## 下一步干什么
模块分离,除了基本的机器人聊天的功能,其他功能尽可能组件化,并且设置响应的注册组件的方式,使后续开发(指接入AI|调用API|其他功能)变得容易

*Progress*
Finish a demo which has integrated a SQLite database for data storage. Has completed basic message receiving functionality and distinguishes between handling personal messages and group messages.

*Next*
Module separation: 
Besides the basicly function of the robot, the other features should be modularized as much as possible. 
Additionally, implement a method for registering components. 
This approach will make future development easier (such as integrating AI, calling APIs, or adding other functionalities) .
